{
  "id": "adv_bond_aoi_01_04",
  "title": "井川葵4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は掃除当番か……。やるのはいいんだ\nでも僕がやると、莉央がたまに怒るんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it my turn to clean today?… It's fine to do it‚\nbut when I do it‚ Rio gets angry sometimes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "え？　どうしてですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "僕の掃除の仕方は大雑把過ぎるんだって\n莉央は細かいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She says my cleaning method is too sloppily\nRio is so meticulous",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "僕は別に気にならないんだけどね\n兄弟がそうだったからそういうものだと思ってたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't really mind\nBut I thought it was normal because my brothers were like that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5333329519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですね。でも大丈夫です！　どんな細かい\n汚れも、これを使えばキレイさっぱり落ちます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ But it's okay! Any tiny bit of dirt\nwill be completely removed with this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.0333329519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "歯ブラシ？　どう使うの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A toothbrush? How can use that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1333329519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "これを使えばですね、部屋のどんなに狭い隙間でも\nキレイに出来るんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With this‚ you can clean even the smallest\ngaps in a room",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2999996186,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6566.667048100001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、こうやって擦れば……\nソファーと床の間も、埃一つなくなりました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See‚ if you scrub like this…\nThere's not a speck of dust between the sofa and the alcove!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1666662853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、こんな方法があったのか\n僕もやってみたいな。その歯ブラシ貸してくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ there was a way like this\nI'd like to try it too‚ Can I borrow that toothbrush?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.8666662853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "はい、どうぞ。私の使い古しなので\nじっと見られると恥ずかしいんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here you go‚ It's my old one‚\nso it's embarrassing if people stare at it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2999996186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　愛の歯ブラシは、これじゃないよね？\nこのピンクのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm? This isn't Ai's toothbrush‚ is it?\nThis pink one is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6666662853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "っ！？　り、り、り、莉央さんのっ！？\nしまった、私、よく見ないで間違えて……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh!? R-R-R-Rio-san's!?\nOh my god‚ I didn't look carefully and made a mistake…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0666662853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "しかもこれ、使い古しじゃなくて\n今使ってるやつだった気がする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And this isn't a used one‚\nif feels like it hasn't been used for long",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9999996186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "今朝も、やっと自分の口に合う歯ブラシを見つけた\nって喜んで出て行ったよ。……ん？　愛、凄い汗だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This morning‚ she went out happily that she finally found\na toothbrush that fits my mouth‚ …Oh? Ai‚ you're sweating so much",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4666662853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "終わった……葵さん、お世話になりました\n私、本日付けでLizNoirを辞めます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's over… Aoi-san‚ thank you for everything\nI'm quitting LizNoir as of today",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8999996186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "待って。それくらいで莉央は愛をクビにはしないよ\n行こう、愛",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ Rio wouldn't fire Ai for something like that\nLet's go‚ Ai",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3333329519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇ……どこにですか？　一緒に逃げるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh… where we go? Are we running away together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.0333329519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "ドラッグストアさ。掃除のついでに消耗品も\n買い足したって言えば誰も文句は言わないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The drugstore‚ No one will complain if I say\nI bought some supplies while I was cleaning",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5333370209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、全員分の歯ブラシも買ってこよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I'll buy toothbrushes for everyone",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.6333370209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ありがとうございます！\n葵さんは、この小美山愛の、命の恩人です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-Thank you!\nAoi-san‚ your my‚ Ai Komiyama's savior!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1666703542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_04-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "まったく大げさだな。ほら、早く行こう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's an exaggeration‚ Hurry‚ let's go",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.4000036876,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}